\newlabel{tab:svm}{{6}{9}{PawSVM comparison across TabbySVM, PurrPoly, and FurRBF. PurrPoly achieves the highest held-out ROC-AUC. FurRBF does not improve over TabbySVM, ruling out the need for a highly flexible local boundary}{table.caption.16}{}}
